      • createFile

        public static MLPrivateFile createFile(String localPath,
                       String remotePath)
        Creates a new file from the local path and specified the remote path on the server.
        参数:
        localPath - The local path represents where the file is on your mobile.
        remotePath - The remote path represents where the file should be on the server.
        返回:
        The MLPrivateFile instance.
